{
  "stem": "1581.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And privately, they always were very friendly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was always just publicly that they had to show some anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I told him the trouble that my brother is in because he's not an Austrian citizen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And within a week, he had his Austrian citizenship.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that was a-- a-- a interesting event, but we never became Austrian citizens, which was-- when I later on went to medical school, was a disadvantage.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Number one, my tuition was much higher, because I was a foreigner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And number two, I was unable to get any kind of a job that paid, because I was not an Austrian.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But later on, I was very happy not to be an Austrian, because I then had to do my military duties, which were two years of service.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I always was very fond of Czechoslovakia, and I was determined to stay there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to what is called in middle Europe, middle school, but here it's called high school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's called a gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I graduated in 1928.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the same year, my father died of a heart attack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I, then, and against my family's wishes, I entered medical school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because my father had died, and we were no longer in very good financial situations, and they wanted me to go out and work and make a living.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I promised them I would not be a burden, and I always worked all through my studies to pay my tuition myself.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no problem to enter medical school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whoever wanted to enter just entered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You just inscribed yourself, and you were a medical student.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was young, and there is nothing more beautiful than to study medicine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
